        "Add a new product as one cart row with quantity 1.",
        "Adding the same product again must increment its existing row instead of creating a duplicate.",
        "Keep different products in separate rows with their own quantities and line totals.",
        "Derive total item count, line totals, and the overall total from the current cart. Format every amount as USD with two decimal places."
      ],
      "frameworkTests": [
