        "Disable both Add to cart and Increase when a cart line reaches its product's stock limit, and never allow either path to exceed stock.",
        "Re-enable Add to cart and Increase after the quantity drops below the limit.",
        "Announce `Wireless Headphones reached its stock limit.` through a stable atomic polite cart status when that limit is reached."
      ],
